  "description": {
    "zh": "那么BTR司机把一切都向你解释清楚了吗？太好了。到目前为止，我们所知道的关于Ref的一切给了我一些想法——你看，他的人和Glukhar的团伙一起工作。这就是你要制造一些骚动的地方，让我解释一下计划。\n\n找到这些人，就攻击他们，我建议你从远处做，他们配合得很好，在他们的环境中可以很快把你搞得一团糟，只要确保别碰团伙头目。",
    "en": "So did the BTR driver explain everything to you? Excellent. Everything we know so far about Ref gave me a few ideas - You see, his people work together with Glukhar's gang. That's where you will cause some distress, let me explain the plan.\n\nLocate these people and just attack them, I suggest you do that from a distance, they are well coordinated and can really mess you up quickly in their environment, just make sure to leave the gang leader alone."
  },
